data.description: USDA Loan ELIGIBLE!!!! Welcome to 35 Poplar Preserve Boulevard! This beautiful 4 Bed, 2.5 Bath, 2 car garage Home in the highly sought-after Poplar Preserve Subdivision is peerless! Located walking distance to the community amenities and parking, also close to shopping, schools, I-85 and Piedmont Newnan hospital! This home is better than new construction! Throughout the main level you'll find LVP flooring and an open concept living space! Perfect for cozy nights by the switch operated functional gas fireplace or large family gatherings! The kitchen features a very large pantry, stone countertops, stainless steel appliances, oversized island with seating for up to 4, huge eat-in area with access to the patio, fully fenced backyard and an open view to the oversized living space! Just past the fireplace you'll find the stairs leading to the second floor, where the oversized owner's suite, sizable secondary bedrooms, laundry room and bathroom are all perfectly laid out! This home is a short drive to EVERYTHING Newnan has to offer, truly move in ready and priced just right! Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity!!!
